# Lesson Access Control

The system uses strict access validation.

Students can only access lessons if:

- The course is purchased
  OR
- The user redeemed a valid access code
  OR
- The lesson is marked as preview

Admins:

- Full access

Teachers:

- Access to their own course lessons

